Modern Browsing is a WP Plugin that shows a non-intrusive, cool bar at the top of your page. When a browser is obsolete by the preferences of the administrator.

Supports:
Internet Explorer (option to add HTML5 Shiv automatically)
Opera
Firefox
Safari

Spanish Translation included and .PO located in /languages/